ers are only accepted by users registered in the system of NIKALEX-M Ltd. More about registration – in the section – Registration.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></p> <p><span data-contrast="auto">Orders of goods and services on the sites are made by adding the desired goods and / or services to the Shopping Cart and following the steps and instructions on the site to complete and submit the relevant order.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></p> <p><span data-contrast="auto">The delivery of goods ordered from the online store is carried out through a courier company with which NIKALEX-M Ltd. has a contractual relations:&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="auto">DHL Express Bulgaria Ltd (</span><a href="http://www.dhl.bg/"><b><span data-contrast="none">www.dhl.bg</span></b></a><b><span data-contrast="none">)&nbsp;</span></b><span data-contrast="auto">and&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="auto">BXB s.r.o.</span><b><span data-contrast="auto">&nbsp;(</span></b><a href="https://boxberry.ru/"><b><span data-contrast="none">https://boxberry.ru</span></b></a><b><span data-contrast="none">)</span></b><b><span data-contrast="auto">.</span></b><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></p> <p><span data-contrast="auto">Deliveries are made only&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="auto">on the geographical territory of the Republic of Bulgaria, which excludes deliveries in Bulgarian diplomatic missions abroad, embassies, ships and aircraft under the Bulgarian flag, etc. which according to the norms of international law are considered part of the territory of the Republic of Bulgaria.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></p> <ul> <li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="20" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="auto">NIKALEKS-M is able to execute orders and outside the territory of the Republic of Bulgaria. In these cases the customer pays in advance to the bank account of NIKALEX-M Ltd. the value of the ordered items, as well as the transport of the ordered goods to the address specified by him.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></li> </ul> <p><span data-contrast="auto">Deliveries made by DHL Express Bulgaria Ltd</span><span data-contrast="auto">&nbsp;and&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="auto">BXB s.r.o.</span><span data-contrast="auto">&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="auto">are always delivered at the expense of the&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="auto">c</span><span data-contrast="auto">u</span><span data-contrast="auto">stomer</span><span data-contrast="auto">,</span><span data-contrast="auto">&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="auto">regardless of the value of the order.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></p> <ul> <li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="20" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="auto">For orders on the territory of the Republic of Bulgaria (up to 2 working days) –&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="auto">5 Euro&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></li> <li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="20" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="3" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="none">For orders outside the territory of the Republic of Bulgaria to European Union countries&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="none">&nbsp;(up to</span><span data-contrast="none">&nbsp;5&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="none">working days) —&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="none">15 Euro</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></li> <li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="20" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="4" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="none">For orders&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="none">only for Russian Federation</span><span data-contrast="none">&nbsp;(up to</span><span data-contrast="none">&nbsp;10&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="none">working days) —&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="none">30 Euro</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:140,&quot;335559740&quot;:276}">&nbsp;</span></li> </ul> <p><span data-contrast="auto">Orders received before 14:00 will be prepared for shipment and delivered&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="auto">on</span><span data-contrast="auto">&nbsp;courier&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="auto">company&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="auto">within the same business day.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></p> <p><span data-contrast="auto">Orders received after 14:00 will be prepared for shipment and delivered&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="auto">on</span><span data-contrast="auto">&nbsp;courier&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="auto">company&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="auto">on the next business day.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></p> <p><span data-contrast="auto">NIKALEX-M Ltd. makes every effort to respect the delivery deadlines, but however cannot guarantee the execution if are affected by reasons beyond the control of the firm.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></p> <p><span data-contrast="auto">Deliveries are are affected by public holidays and weekends.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></p> <p><span data-contrast="auto">The execution of an order may be hindered for any of the following reasons:</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></p> <ul> <li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="21" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="auto">One or more of the goods ordered are not available; in this case an employee of NIKALEX-M Ltd. establishes contact with the customer and offers alternatives in case the ordered goods cannot be delivered on time.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></li> <li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="21" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="auto">No payment has been made (or there is a delay in payment) by the user if he has chosen bank transfer or payment of the amount due via an electronic payment instrument.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></li> <li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="21" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="3" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="auto">The customer has specified an incorrect or incomplete delivery address.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></li> <li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="21" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="4" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="auto">No telephone number for contact with the client or wrong and inaccessible one.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></li> </ul> <p><span data-contrast="auto">In case of problems related to the delivery due to the fault of NIKALEX-M Ltd., all additional costs will be borne by the company. In all other cases subsequent dispatch of the shipment will be charged at the expense of the recipient.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></p> <p><span data-contrast="auto">The goods are delivered to the recipients by hand against a signature, and in the case of large shipments (at the discretion of the courier) they are delivered to the entrance of the building. In case of impossibility or difficulty for delivery in person to the addressee, the consignments shall be delivered as follows:</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></p> <ul> <li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="22" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="auto">for business address – to a person with a place of work at the address, indicating the name and position</span><span data-contrast="auto">&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="auto">/ department of the person who received the consignment.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></li> <li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="22" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="auto">for home address – to a member of the household, indicating the name of the person who received the shipment, and its relationship with the recipient.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:252}">&nbsp;</span></li> </ul> <p><span data-contrast="auto">In case of impossibility to deliver the shipment during the first visit, which is not due to NIKALEX-M Ltd. and / or the courier (in case no one is at the address, etc.), the courier leaves a notice indicating a contact phone number, to which the recipient can call back within three working days in order to specify a new deadline for delivery. In case of impossibility to deliver the shipment also during the second visit, which is not due to NIKALEX-M Ltd. and / or the courier, the distance transaction contract is automatically terminated, and in this case, as a sanction for non-pe